<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>DIN – About</title>
  
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@200;300;400;500&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/DIN.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/style.css">
</head>
<body>

<!-- CUSTOM CURSOR -->
<div class="din-cursor" id="dinCursor"></div>
<div class="din-cursor-ring" id="dinCursorRing"></div>

<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="about-hero">
  <div class="about-hero-inner">
    <div class="about-hero-photo fu">
      <img src="/assets/images/me.jpg" alt="Din portrait">
    </div>
    <p class="about-eyebrow fu d1">Creative Designer &amp; Developer</p>
    <h1 class="fu d2">Crafting <em>digital</em><br>experiences</h1>
    <p class="about-hero-sub fu d3">
      Driven by curiosity and a love for design, I build simple, functional and visually striking interfaces — where creativity meets technology.
    </p>
    <div class="scroll-indicator fu d4">
      <span>Scroll</span>
      <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="about" class="about-bio">
  <div class="about-bio-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="about-bio-label">About me</p>
      <h2>Design is my<br>language</h2>

      <p>
        As a student and self-driven designer, I constantly explore new ideas and dive deeper into modern design principles. Every project is an opportunity to learn, experiment, and push the boundaries of what's possible on screen.
      </p>

      <p>
        I use most of my expertise at the intersection of design and front-end development — building experiences that are both beautiful and functional.
      </p>

      <a href="/gallery" class="more-link">
        View my work
        <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="about-bio-right">
      <p class="about-bio-label">Certificates</p>
      <div class="skills-list">
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-name">Web Design</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">SkillBox</span>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-name">Interactive Media Design</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Seneca College</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="about-bio-label" style="margin-top:28px">Tools &amp; Skills</p>
      <div class="skills-list">
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-name">Adobe Creative Suite</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Ps · Ai · Id · Ae · XD</span>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-name">UI / UX Design</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Figma</span>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-name">Front-End Development</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">HTML · CSS · JS</span>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-name">3D Modelling</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Blender</span>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-name">Motion Graphics</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">After Effects</span>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-name">Graphic Design</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Print · Brand Identity</span>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-name">Responsive Design</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Mobile-first</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-cta">
  <small>That's all for now.</small>
  <h2>Got a project in mind?</h2>
  <h3>Let's talk</h3>

  <div class="cta-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="cta-field">
        <label>Email</label>
        <p>din.design.studio@gmail.com</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-field">
        <label>Phone</label>
        <p>+1 (000) 000-0000</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-btn-wrap">
      <button class="cta-btn" onclick="window.location='/contact'">Get in touch</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="site-footer__inner">
    <div class="site-footer__col site-footer__col--brand">
      <img src="/assets/DIN.png" alt="DIN Logo" class="site-footer__logo-img">
      <p class="site-footer__tagline">Creative designer &amp; developer crafting digital experiences that matter.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="site-footer__col">
      <p class="site-footer__col-title">Navigation</p>
      <nav class="site-footer__nav">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/gallery">Gallery</a>
        <a class="is-active" href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="site-footer__col">
      <p class="site-footer__col-title">Contact</p>
      <div class="site-footer__item">din.design.studio@gmail.com</div>
      <div class="site-footer__item">Canada</div>
    </div>

    <div class="site-footer__col">
      <p class="site-footer__col-title">Newsletter</p>
      <p class="site-footer__form-label">Stay updated with new projects and design insights.</p>
      <form class="site-footer__form" id="newsletterForm">
        <input id="newsletterEmail" type="email" placeholder="your@email.com">
        <button type="submit">Subscribe</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="site-footer__bottom">
    <span>© 2025 DIN. All rights reserved.</span>
    <span>Designed &amp; built with care</span>
  </div>
</footer>

<script src="/assets/js/main.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>